      "path": "skills/posclient/add-posclient-automation.md",
      "plugin": "posclient",
      "entity": "order",
      "action": "automation",
      "triggers": [
        "trigger action",
        "webhook",
        "event broker",
        "message broker",
        "automation rules"
      ],
      "description": "the wish adds a new automation **trigger** (a posclient event other workflows can react to) or a new automation **action** (a step a workflow can execute on posclient data) — e.g., \"trigger when a Order hits Won stage,\" \"action: append a checklist when a Order moves stage.\""
    },
    {
      "path": "skills/posclient/add-posclient-graphql-query.md",
      "plugin": "posclient",
      "entity": "order",
      "action": "graphql-query",
      "triggers": [
        "graphql query",
        "fetch list",
        "get detail",
        "total count",
        "read endpoint"
      ],
      "description": "the wish needs a new GraphQL **read** on a posclient entity that the existing `orders`/`orderDetail`/`pipelines`/`stages` queries can't serve — e.g., `ordersByPriority`, `ordersClosingThisWeek`, `pipelineHealthSummary`."
    },
    {
      "path": "skills/posclient/add-posclient-mutation.md",
      "plugin": "posclient",
      "entity": "order",
      "action": "mutation",
      "triggers": [
        "graphql mutation",
        "create record",
        "update record",
        "delete record",
        "remove item"
      ],
      "description": "the wish needs a new GraphQL **write** on a posclient entity that the existing `ordersAdd` / `ordersEdit` / `ordersChange` / `ordersArchive` / `ordersRemove` set doesn't cover — e.g., `ordersBulkArchive(_ids)`, `ordersAssignBatch(_ids, userId)`, `ordersConvertToTemplate(_id)`."
    },
    {
      "path": "skills/posclient/add-posclient-segment-field.md",
      "plugin": "posclient",
      "entity": "order",
      "action": "segment-field",
      "triggers": [
        "segment filter",
        "elastic filter",
        "search criteria",
        "segment builder"
      ],
      "description": "the wish makes an existing Order field filterable in the segment builder — e.g., \"I want to build a segment of orders where `priority` is `high`,\" or \"let me filter by `closeDate < today`.\" The field must already exist (or be added first via [`./add-order-field.md`](./add-order-field.md))."
    },
    {
      "path": "skills/posclient/add-posclient-trpc-procedure.md",
      "plugin": "posclient",
      "entity": "order",
      "action": "trpc-procedure",
      "triggers": [
        "trpc route",
        "internal api",
        "cross-plugin rpc",
        "router procedure"
      ],
      "description": "the wish exposes posclient data/behavior to **another plugin** via type-safe RPC — e.g., `posclient.order.ordersForCustomer(customerId)` so frontline can show \"open orders\" inside a conversation card, or `posclient.pos.activeTerminals()` so operation can list POS-affected branches. NOT for UI-only data flow (that's GraphQL) and NOT for fire-and-forget events (that's Redis pubsub — see [`../../rules/20-architecture-boundaries.md`](../../rules/20-architecture-boundaries.md))."
    },
